<p><strong>SCP-CN-1172：</strong>纸中世界<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/parabola-x" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6217553); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6217553&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607687147" alt="Parabola_X" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6217553)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/parabola-x" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6217553); return false;">Parabola_X</a></span><br />
